column8: PAS vice-president Iskandar Samad stressed that PAS state assemblypersons in Selangor cannot be bought in an attempt to topple the state government."As a senior exco in the Selangor government, I would like to reiterate that PAS exco members and state assemblypersons in Selangor cannot be bought to bring down the state government of the day."No amount of money can buy any exco or state assemblypersons so that they will form a new government with Umno," he said in a statement today...Read more: https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/381796#ixzz4gfVuySr6
cukur selangor ppl have pas ppl.
